{"id":56824,"title":"[Evaluation of the macular ganglion cell layer by spectral-domain optical coherence tomography in diagnosis of early-stage glaucoma].","abstract":"The new Cirrus HD-OCT software was used to measure the thickness of ganglion cell and inner plexiform layers (GCIPL) in macular region in 56 patients (56 eyes) with early-stage primary open-angle glaucoma (POAG) and 53 healthy controls (53 eyes). The diagnostic value of the best parameters of GCIPL for POAG detection was insignificantly lower as compared to the best parameters of the peripapillary retinal nerve fiber layer and optic nerve head.","date":"2014-03-14","categories":"Eye Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24624796","annotations":[{"name":"Optical coherence tomography","weight":0.913439,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optical_coherence_tomography"},{"name":"Ganglion cell","weight":0.906012,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ganglion_cell"},{"name":"Glaucoma","weight":0.872951,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glaucoma"},{"name":"Optic nerve","weight":0.868774,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optic_nerve"},{"name":"Cell (biology)","weight":0.804197,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cell_(biology)"},{"name":"Nervous system","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nervous_system"},{"name":"Macula of retina","weight":0.773888,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Macula_of_retina"},{"name":"Medical diagnosis","weight":0.707268,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_diagnosis"},{"name":"Ganglion cell layer","weight":0.651453,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ganglion_cell_layer"},{"name":"Tomography","weight":0.62749,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tomography"},{"name":"Retinal","weight":0.579861,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Retinal"},{"name":"Optic disc","weight":0.5792